OL,7,FUK politicians could be inspired to
OL,8,Freplicate Donald Trump's "extreme
OL,9,Ftransparency", the country's former
OL,10,Ftop civil servant has said.
OL,12,FSimon Case, who served as Cabinet
OL,13,FSecretary for four years, praised the
OL,14,FUS president's "impressive political
OL,15,Ftheatre" in signing a raft of
OL,16,Fexecutive orders that range from
OL,17,Ftrade, immigration and civil rights
OL,18,Fsince returning to office on Monday.
