OL,3,CUK politicians may follow Trump's
OL,4,Capproach, former Civil Service chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"It is harder to imagine a British
OL,8,Fprime minister filling a stadium with
OL,9,Fadoring fans to witness the signature
OL,10,Fof memos instructing Whitehall to do
OL,11,Fthis or that.
OL,13,F"Nevertheless, the extreme
OL,14,Ftransparency of Trump's approach might
OL,15,Fbe something that more politicians in
OL,16,Fthe UK are willing to try in future,
OL,17,Fgiven the declining public interest in
OL,18,Fand trust in politics."
