OL,3,CUK politicians may follow Trump's
OL,4,Capproach, former Civil Service chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIn the first hours of his presidency,
OL,8,FMr Trump pardoned hundreds of people
OL,9,Ffor their roles in the January 6 2021
OL,10,Friot at the US Capitol, withdrew the
OL,11,FUS from the Paris climate accords and
OL,12,Fthe World Health Organisation,
OL,13,Fdeclared a national emergency at the
OL,14,FUS-Mexico border, and sought to end
OL,15,Fautomatic citizenship for anyone born
OL,16,Fin America.
OL,18,FHe also signed an order that intends
OL,19,Fto pause a ban on TikTok for 75 days
OL,20,Fto give its China-based parent company
OL,21,Fmore time to find an approved buyer.
